item.title: By: barbaralukas
item.dc:creator: barbaralukas
item.description: Congratulations to Yvonne for well deserved recognition. I ended up subscribing to the magazine to get a copy as I was unable to find it in Ottawa, Canada. Am trying her technique on a few trees of my own most significantly the maple tree. After five months - there is some success happening.
